{"type":"answer","id":36032,"parentType":"question","parentId":8501,"uid":5719,"contents":"昨晚我开着AE89，上了steam山，发现入口有一道坡，虽然引擎得到了改装，但车身很轻很容易打滑，我一个油门一个挂挡翻了过去，可惜如我所料打滑了，后来我喝了瓶酸奶直接飞进山间，大家的车速都很快，他们看到我就问我是不是喝了番蔷汤，我摆了摆手，一个下水道过弯……<br>\n谁对国行充满希望？14年大战后主机玩国行的有几个？<br>\n全世界失望即将开动。<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0zC9ua.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0zC9ua.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/w0zC9ua.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TEavif9.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TEavif9.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TEavif9.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-10","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}